This is a template of a blog using nanoc. It can be used to easily deploy a new
statically generated blog with nanoc, including some already implemented
features:
 - posts pagination;
 - twitter, facebook and google+ buttons;
 - intense debate comments;
 - google analytics;
 - twitter bootstrap theme;
 - tags on sidebar;
 - atom feeds;

Installation
============

Just install nanoc and some more gems to build it. Then, on the root folder,
run:

 nanoc co
 nanoc view (only if you want to run the local server)

gems dependency:
 - builder
 - nokogiri - dependencies required (rdoc, rdoc-data, libxslt)
 - coderay
 - kramdown
 - adsf (run local server for debugging)
